official_title: A resolution to establish a bipartisan group of Senators to be known as the Senate GATT Negotiations Observer Group.
short_title: Senate GATT Negotiations Observer Group Resolution

summary.text: Senate GATT Negotiations Observer Group Resolution - Establishes a bipartisan group of Senators to be known as the Senate GATT Negotiations Observer Group to monitor the conclusion of the Uruguay round of GATT (General Agreement on Tariffs and Trade) negotiations. Terminates the Group upon the adjournment sine die of the 103d Congress.
